@startuml
title UC01 - Realizar Autenticação (Login)

' Configuração visual melhorada
hide footbox
autoactivate off
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #374151
    LifeLineBorderColor #9CA3AF
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5FF
    ActorBorderColor #374151
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    DatabaseBorderColor #374151
    DatabaseBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
    BoxBorderColor #9CA3AF
    BoxBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    GroupBorderColor #9CA3AF
    GroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    ActivationBorderColor #111827
    ActivationBackgroundColor #CFE3FF
    ParticipantPadding 28
    BoxPadding 10
    MessageAlign center
}
skinparam maxMessageSize 70

actor Usuario as U
boundary "Tela de Login
Next.js" as Front
control "AuthController
Micronaut" as Auth
control "UsuarioRepository" as Repo
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

U -> Front: Informa e-mail e senha
activate Front
note right of Front
  Valida campos obrigatórios
  e prepara o payload.
end note

Front -> Auth: POST /auth/login
{email, senha}
activate Auth
Auth -> Repo: findByEmail(email)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: SELECT usuario WHERE email = ?
activate DB
DB --> Repo: Dados do usuário
deactivate DB
Repo --> Auth: Usuario encontrado
deactivate Repo

alt Credenciais válidas
    note right of Auth
      Identifica o tipo de usuário:
      Aluno, Professor ou Empresa.
    end note
    Auth --> Front: 200 OK
{id, nome, tipoUsuario}
    deactivate Auth
    note right of Front
      Armazena usuário autenticado
      e define a rota do painel.
    end note
    Front --> U: Redireciona para painel do perfil
else Credenciais inválidas
    Auth --> Front: 401 Unauthorized
{erro}
    deactivate Auth
    Front --> U: Exibe toast de erro
end

deactivate Front
@enduml
